OL,5, Blue star Lee Ryan has been handed a   
OL,6, 12-month suspended prison sentence for 
OL,7, racially abusing a cabin crew member on
OL,8, a British Airways flight.              
OL,10,FRyan, 40, was found guilty in January  
OL,11,Fof racially aggravated common assault  
OL,12,Fby beating and behaving in an abusive  
OL,13,Fway towards the cabin crew member.     
OL,15,FHe had earlier admitted being drunk on 
OL,16,Fthe flight from Glasgow to London after
OL,17,Fdrinking a bottle of port.             
OL,19,FFor that offence he was handed a       
OL,20,Fconcurrent four-month suspended term.  
